    <attracc>
      <attraccr>The hsg_UCRB_Daymet_resolution.txt ASCII grid combines information from gSSURGO (where available) and STATSGO2 datasets, which was then resampled to match the Daymet climate data resolution (1000m).</attraccr>
    </attracc>
    <logic>Quality assurance was performed by project hydrologist by comparing resampled HSG dataset to original datasets.</logic>
    <complete>Data are complete.  ASCII grid cellsize is 1000 meters.</complete>
